      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Infobox monarch
|name            =Abbas II Hilmi
|title           =[[Khedive]] of [[Egypt]] and [[Sudan]]&lt;br&gt;
[[Image:Regno d'Egitto.gif|150px]]
|image           =[[Image:Abbas Hilmi II.JPG|200px]]
