==Cultural references==
Ajaigarh fort has been sold to [[Oberoi Hotels &amp; Resorts|Oberoi Group]] and they plan to develop a tiger resort there. It is considered a pet project of &quot;Bikki&quot; Oberoi son of Mr. [[Mohan Singh Oberoi]].

