ak |year=1999 |publisher=Central European University Press |location=Budapest |isbn=9789639116672 |page=162 |chapter=A glimpse of openness in medieval society: Al-Ḥakam II of Córdoba and his non-Muslim collaborators}}&lt;/ref&gt; (favorite)
