| signature       =
| religion        = [[Sunni Islam]] ([[Maliki]] [[Madh'hab|school]])&lt;ref&gt;{{cite book |last=Daftary |first=Farhad |title=The Isma'ilis: Their History and Doctrines |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=kQGlyZAy134C&amp;pg=PA173 |year=1992 |publisher=Cambridge University Press |isbn=9780521429740 |page=173 |quote=... the Umayyad ʿAbd al-Raḥmān III, who was a Mālikī Sunnī.}}&lt;/ref&gt;
